Class AlarmKeyResultImpl

java.lang.Object
  ossj.qos.fmri.AlarmKeyResultImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
javax.oss.fm.monitor.AlarmKeyResult, javax.oss.ManagedEntityKeyResult, java.io.Serializable, javax.oss.SerializerFactory
public class AlarmKeyResultImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.oss.fm.monitor.AlarmKeyResult

AlarmKeyResultImpl Represents the result of an operation on a set of alarm values. It contains the alarm reference, a pass or fail status, and an exception if the result failed.
